      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MONEY KEEPING (6) was strongly fancied on the back of a win two starts back but finished second last time (29.82) at this track. Has good speed so she should be prominent despite the draw. Capable of going well again. STATUS JEWEL (7) was below best at her last start when 6th at this track following a win (29.81) there two back. Form here at this distance is sound. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Must be included in calculations. ZIPPING VIOLET (1) three runs back clocked a scintillating 22.48 win over 401m at Richmond then has found the minor money in two runs since. Expected to feature on best figures. SUMMER ANGEL (4) was impressive in a head turning 29.58 win last start. Each way chance.",
